description: Ten of 26 rare animals from Mexico discovered at a German airport did not survive.
title: Reptiles smuggled from Mexico found at German airport stitched inside dolls
title_page: Reptiles smuggled from Mexico found at German airport stitched inside dolls - BBC News
maintext: It is not yet clear if they came from the wild or from captive breeding programmes. They were in two packages seized on 30 October and 8 November.
